comment._content: [http://www.flickr.com/photos/beachcomberaustralia] Ha! If I remember rightly Sam's son Ted helped the library caption the collection when they were donated to the Mitchell Library. He got a few wrong, such as a sequence of Ultimo slum clearance photos he id'd as The Rocks. In any case, the library catalogue gives a date of "about 1929". A pretty good guess considering it turns out to be 28 October 1928.
